name: Vessels 082: Princess Martha
description: Unable to have children of her own, The Queen has had a number of adopted ‘daughters’ upon whom she has bestowed the title of ‘princess’. The life of a princess is a glamourous and opulent one, but rarely very lengthy. It’s all too easy to draw The Queen’s ire. Knowing this, Princess Martha lives each day as if it is her last. But not in a fun way, in more of a ‘living in constant fear’ kind of way.
